nodes.text: The D-11 water speeder was a 7-meter long pleasure speeder designed by the Theed Palace Space Vessel Engineering Corps. Although designed to navigate on water rather than space, it shared many similarities with the N-1 starfighter, which was also build by the Engineering Corps. Such speeders were built specially for the monarch of Naboo and their entourage, and were kept in a section of the royal boathouse of Theed.
